    ) a

group by pogMarketingFeedBaseTab
","temp.nmso_bau")

run(sql="

with cte as(
SELECT * FROM(
SELECT distinct pogId as pogs
FROM `temp.nmso_bau` 
WHERE NM3SO<=10)p

JOIN(
    SELECT *
    FROM `temp.FB_Live_New_Feed`
    where availability = 'in stock') fb
ON p.pogs = fb.dmPublisherInfoId

LEFT JOIN `last14Days(agCmDump)` b 
on p.pogs=b.pogId

left join (select subOrderId as subo, Channel from `temp.order_sd`) c 
    on b.subOrderId=c.subo
    where DATEDIFF(current_date(),to_date(FROM_UNIXTIME((b.orderDate)/1000)))BETWEEN 1 and 3)
    
select count(distinct pogs) as In_Stock_LTE10_pogs,
        count(distinct case when lower(Channel) like 'fb%' then subo end)/3 as FB_ADS_LTE10,
        count(distinct case when lower(Channel) like 'fb%' and DATEDIFF(current_date(),to_date(FROM_UNIXTIME((orderDate)/1000)))=1 then subo end) as FB_DS_LTE10
from cte
",1000)
